<!doctype html>
<html class="no-js" lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  </head>
    <header>
<div class="row full-width center-parent" id="header2" >
  <div class="small-5 columns small-center">
    <h1 class="" style="font-size:45px">Rules On Wheels</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="small-6 columns small-centered" style:"vertical-align: bottom">
  <div class="top-bar-right" style:"vertical-align: bottom">
    <ul class="menu" style:"vertical-align: bottom">
      <% if logged_in? %>
       <li style="background-color:#f1c40f;color:#333;"><a class="" style="background-color:#f1c40f;color:#333;" href=<%=root_path%> id="playButton"><i class="icon-home"></i>Home</a></li>
        <li><a class="" href=<%=game_path%>  id="playButton"><i class="icon-gamepad"></i>Play</a></li>
        <li><a class="" href=<%=highscores_path%>  id="playButton"><i class="icon-up-bold"></i>Top 10</a></li>
        <li><a class="" href=<%=quiz_path%>  id="playButton"><i class="icon-doc-text"></i>Quiz</a></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Log out", logout_path, method: "delete", id: "playButton", class: "icon-cancel-squared"%></li>
    <% else %>
        <li><a class="" href=<%=root_path%> id="playButton"><i class="icon-home"></i>Home</a></li>
        <li><a class="" href=<%=login_path%> id="playButton"><i class="icon-lock"></i>Log in</a></li>
        <li><a class="" href=<%=signup_path%> id="playButton"><i class="icon-user-add"></i>Sign up</a></li>
    <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
  </header>
  <body>
    <div class="row full-width center" >
      <div class="large-12 columns large-centered">
        <p style="color:#333;font-weight:bold;font-size:24px"> Welcome <b style="color:#DAA520"><%= @user.name %></b>, your highest score so far is <b style = "color:#DAA520"><%= @user.score %></b>, try to break it ;)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row full-width center" >
      <div class="large-12 columns large-centered">
        <% if @user.score >= 20000 %>
            <img src= '<%= asset_path 'Gold.png' %>' style="height:60px;width:60px">
        <% elsif @user.score >= 15000 %>
            <img src= '<%= asset_path 'Silver.png' %>' style="height:60px;width:60px">
        <% elsif @user.score >= 10000 %>
            <img src= '<%= asset_path 'Bronze.png' %>' style="height:60px;width:60px">
        <% else %>
            <p style="color:#333;font-weight:bold;font-size:24px"> You have no medals yet </p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row section" id="about">
      <div class="large-3 columns small-centered"> 
        <h4 class="title center" style = "color:#DAA520">About</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row section">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="large-1 columns">
            <b style="color:#4169E1;font-size:50px"><i class="icon-cab"></i></b>    
          </div>
          <div class="large-5 columns">
            <b style = "color:#333">About the Game</b>
              <p>The game is dedicated to teach the public about traffic law. The game takes place in a training area where the player is trying to get a driving license. The player has to pickup examiners from one place to another and after the examiner reaches the desired destination, the player has to answer the theoretical part of the exam, which is identify some traffic signs. This cycle goes on till the time expires. The more questions you answer and the faster you drive the examiner, the higher your score will be.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="large-1 columns">
            <b style="font-size:55px"><i style = "color:#808080" class="icon-steering-wheel"></i></b>
          </div >
          <div class="large-5 columns">
            <b style= "color:#333">Instructions</b>
            <p> You have to go to the yellow halo and stop inside it. A green halo will appear and you must go to the green halo as fast as possible, the more time you save the higher your score. Up arrow for acceleration, down button for deceleration, left and right arrows for turning left and right. There is no turning left or right unless the car is accelerating or decelrating. The shift button is used to activate the nitrous.</p>
          </div >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row expanded section" id="game">
      <div class="large-12 columns">



        <!-- PUT YOUR GAME INSIDE HERE-->




      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row section" id="gwap">
      <div class="large-3 columns small-centered"> 
        <h4 class="title center" style = "color:#DAA520">GWAP Cluster</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row section" id="gwapContent">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="large-4 columns">
            <b style="font-size:44px;color:#5F9EA0"><i class="icon-info"></i></b>
            <br>
            <b style="color:#333">Who we are?</b>
            <p>We are the games with a purpose cluster in the GUC.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="large-4 columns">
            <b style="font-size:44px;color:#B22222"><i class="icon-heart"></i></b>
            <br>
            <b style="color:#333">What we do?</b>
            <p>We come up with new serious games ideas, implement them and test them out.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="large-4 columns">
            <b style="font-size:44px;color:#DAA520"><i class="icon-gamepad"></i></b>
            <br>
            <b style = "color:#333">What is a serious game?</b>
            <p>A serious game is a game designed for a primary purpose other than pure entertainment</p>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row footer section expanded" id="footer">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <p>Made by Sherif Ismail of the <b>GWAP</b> Cluster of the GUC</p>
      </div>
    </div>
</html>
